%C A133825 T(n,k) =  min(n*(n+1)/2,k*(k+1)/2), n, k >0.  The order of the list T(n,k) is by sides of squares from T(1,n) to T(n,n), then from T(n,n) to T(n,1). - _Boris Putievskiy_, Jan 13 2013
